"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-28-Refugee-Olympic-team-bids-for-first-ever-medal-1vwMWWLoFG0-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Natalie Carney in Leimen  Copied  A total of 36 athletes from 11 different countries will be representing this year's Olympic refugee team in France.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.998427147177588, \"rank\": 0.0015099576867197454, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThe team was created in 2015 to represent the world's displaced population of over 100 million people.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2016 Games in Rio the team comprised ten athletes.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9994428811336533, \"rank\": 0.0005574294209133452, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That number increased to 29 for Tokyo 2020, which took place in 2021 after the global pandemic caused the Games' postponement.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999986122350836, \"rank\": 1.3877235710955863e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of this year's refugee team is 27-year-old Iranian-born kayaker Saman Soltani.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\", \"score\": 0.847896726166218, \"rank\": 0.17938891507835705, \"text\": \"Saman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"I am proud of who I am,\\\" she told CGTN while describing where she won the many medals hanging on her bedroom wall in Vienna.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"score\": 0.9999998637658885, \"rank\": 1.3609740129454004e-07, \"text\": \"Vienna\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c  Iranian-born kayaker Saman Soltani (left) opens her canoe with her team.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\", \"score\": 0.847896726166218, \"rank\": 0.17938891507835705, \"text\": \"Saman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samaveda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/AFP  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cSoltani grew up in the water.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She started swimming at the age of five, moving into artistic swimming a few years later and becoming Iranian national champion for ten years in a row.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\", \"score\": 0.8540289013662977, \"rank\": 0.17091564870438267, \"text\": \"Iranian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet artistic swimming for girls was frowned upon in her home country, and she was not allowed to compete internationally.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThis is where Soltani's love for kayaking began, leading her to win multiple medals for the national team and taking her abroad.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c  Soltani arrived in Austria in 2022 and quickly found success as a kayaker in her host country and was chosen for the Olympic refugee team in May 2024.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9997884027101617, \"rank\": 0.00020487718850662444, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This time it's like a big mission for me because it's not only for me, it's for my family, for my friends, for everyone who helped me to stand up again,\\\"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c she said.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Iranian-born weightlifter Yekta Jamali Galeh.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yekta Jamali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CGTN  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThe same could be said for another Iranian-born Olympic refugee team member, Yekta Jamali Galeh, who is training as a weightlifter in the German city of Leimen.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yekta Jamali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yekta_Jamali\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9396231206471657, \"rank\": 0.0634628785481279, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1920, \"end\": 1926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leimen_(Baden)\", \"score\": 0.7967373417922383, \"rank\": 0.221729490022209, \"text\": \"Leimen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leimen_(Baden)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leimen_(Baden)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Galeh came to stay in Germany at the age of 17.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"I came to Germany by plane,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9982279101280582, \"rank\": 0.0016056314967544342, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9982279101280582, \"rank\": 0.0016056314967544342, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had the feeling of fear, excitement, stress, all this, but at that moment I was thinking really strong mentally.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really scared, but at that time my fear was not so great.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud of myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE  Rise of the Far Right: Immigration puts Europe at a crossroads  Just for the record: 85-year-old Pole Vika shows DJing's not just a young person's game  Paris 2024: Cleaning the Seine  Galeh watched by Germany's national weightlifting coach Almir Velagic.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.999999999564352, \"rank\": 4.350154243414622e-10, \"text\": \"DJing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}, {\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5166771768082527e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9982279101280582, \"rank\": 0.0016056314967544342, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\", \"score\": 0.9751530325641993, \"rank\": 0.025392943405632487, \"text\": \"Almir\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CGTN  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cTwo years on, Galeh has learnt the German language and is training six days a week with Germany's national weightlifting coach Almir Velagic.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2544, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9999999998094609, \"rank\": 1.8585982492320152e-10, \"text\": \"German language\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9982279101280582, \"rank\": 0.0016056314967544342, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\", \"score\": 0.9751530325641993, \"rank\": 0.025392943405632487, \"text\": \"Almir\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Nelson_de_Almeida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cHe says Galeh's success, and that of many on the refugee team, comes from the strength of her character.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained CGTN: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"The story that she has behind her, what she has achieved, if everyone were to put themselves in this situation at the age of 17, getting on a plane and not knowing where you will end up?\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You need a lot of courage and that is what they have been through their whole life.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People like that have something special in them that will help them to benefit more in regular life and in sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A quote found on one of Galeh's social media pages reads \\\"history will remember everything you do\\\".\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She elaborated on those words for CGTN, explaining that \\\"even if people forget that person and what she did, history never forgets and that is important.\\\"\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThis year's Olympic refugee team, includes athletes from Syria, Afghanistan and Sudan, who will compete in 12 different sports during the 17 day international multi-sport event.\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3487, \"end\": 3492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"score\": 0.5542707672601789, \"rank\": 0.8040724579967465, \"text\": \"Syria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\"}, {\"begin\": 3494, \"end\": 3505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9727198431271264, \"rank\": 0.027078379666512623, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 3510, \"end\": 3515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999973479897258, \"rank\": 2.642549791930683e-06, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 202